Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Layer:10 LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的事實 就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音…玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我會變成真神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所認定的神絕對不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白肉體是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的意思 只是把肉體放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說千砂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這種地方 我不存在也沒所謂）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓網絡協議進化的更趨完整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你的確做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但協議也只是協議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已在更高層次之處加上我才知道的密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把情報放在那資料裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣的情報呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我和那英利政美的思想 履歷 記錄 情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做到底有何意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以匿名的方式存在於網絡上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能永遠生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能控制網上的數據 支配一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種存在方式 應該稱呼為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實神是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是能以普通的方式存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在上位的話 也不能稱為神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 它是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 是被做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不再需要肉體了 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 把書收進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何突然變成如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做錯過什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不敢胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但果然還是變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我真的不該擁有肉體？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這現實世界已不再需要有你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你道別了 玲音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的工作已完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在短短的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒好好對待妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此你自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其實從開始你就自由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能跟你說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有一般家庭的融洽生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但曾是玲音父親的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到非常光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要留下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你不只是一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你到網絡上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會有人來歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該是這樣子的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什麼？玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的世界 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是否做了個假的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據東方傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士團的起源似乎是圓桌騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在還沒有互聯網時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們利用人與人之間所構成的網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來收集所需要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什麼？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS…KNIGHTS到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想知道嗎？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為作為計算機網絡上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定要擁有崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到別的地方好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得這很無聊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 要不要來我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌幸你不來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎不會跟你這種小鬼玩的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話 你也是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩年輕是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡新聞說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說名單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼名單？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS成員的名單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在網絡上流傳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我替他注射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽我在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個換媽媽你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快來的話我就繼續玩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽你好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要繼續玩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天世界各地出現連串自殺事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地警方正全力追查原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺身亡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據消息報導
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是網絡上一個名叫KNIGHTS的組織之中的成員…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為何要這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是我們客戶的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把全世界的KNIGHTS成員找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就負責一切善後工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上世界並非特別的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量只是真實世界的某部份備案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你在網上已全無存在目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已平安無事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得你像是有守護神在保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天那英利政美殘留的計算機程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要它從網絡上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那位顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要我們將那程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠消失在網絡上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…不需要神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 無論現實或網上都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法瞭解你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可說是很不可思議的…感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些崇拜的人已不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼照你所說的 神已經不存在了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是所有人都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要還有一個崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就還是能當神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭啊 就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還能以你所存在 都是我的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本就是網絡的創造者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是網上的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡童話的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界的巖倉玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個程序
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類所做出來的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本沒有一個實體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的家人 假的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 全是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是這樣的
